General.Name: fidentiaX
General.Description: fidentiaX is a marketplace for tradable insurance policies. Their vision is to create a trading marketplace and repository of insurance policies for the masses by leveraging blockchain technology.The fidentiaX token (FDX) is a ERC20 token based on the Ethereum Network.
